release_note: Performance upgrades. Thanks for supporting Brown Sugar!
Usability fixes. Adds support for deleting account from within the app.

Dig this we kicked the search bug to the curb! And now you can get the low down on your account! See the email address associated with your account and your subscription expiration date using the all new My Account page.
